AlgoTrader

Class Dispatcher

  • java.lang.Object
    • AlgoTrader.Dispatcher

  • public class Dispatcher
extends java.lang.Object
    High level object which initiates all necessary components:
    • Read and initialize list of all fin-securities which will be used to as price indicators and/or traded
    • Start GUI (TraderGUI), which aggregates and presents all needed information
    • Initiates a link connection (IBLink) with trading systems. These can be data feeds and/or order execution platforms
    • FileManager consistently handles all i/o streams
    Singleton.
